       3. The character's face MUST come 100% from FACE_REFERENCE only.`
    : `IDENTITY: Adult Vietnamese ${gender} matching description: "${characterDescription}".`;

  // !!! ABSOLUTE OUTFIT FIDELITY RULE !!!
